{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/Title.png?t=1727072457\" /><i>Astra Sentinel is a single-player RTS in which you will be able to test your skills as a strategist and defend humanity from extinction. When you start a game you will have to regain control of the infected planets in the solar system. Once you have colonized a planet, build on its surface by switching from a planetary to a space view without loading screens. Enjoy an epic campaign mode or prove your worth in the infinitely replayable skirmish mode.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/Divider.png?t=1727072457\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/Headline_02_EN.png?t=1727072457\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/Gif_01.gif?t=1727072457\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face an endless horde of aliens who seek only to infect all worlds in their path.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create lines of defense between your planets, take advantage of the coverage of asteroid belts, place energy shields, deploy space turrets and fight against extinction.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Go on the attack at the right time and reconquer planets to increase your production lines.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/Headline_01_EN.png?t=1727072457\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/Gif_02.gif?t=1727072457\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reconquer worlds infected by an alien plague.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore solar systems and find different types of planets, from icy worlds to desert wastelands.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build on the planetary surface and return to the space view without loading screens!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/Headline_03_EN.png?t=1727072457\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/Gif_03.gif?t=1727072457\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an epic campaign in which you will have to regain control of several solar systems around the galaxy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prove your worth in skirmish mode. Adjust the parameters to your liking and randomly generate a different solar system in each game for infinite replayability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face numerous difficulty levels that will test your strategist skills.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/Divider.png?t=1727072457\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/extras/CallToAction_EN.png?t=1727072457\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727072457","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/page.bg.jpg?t=1727072457","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171790/083dba8c6a4f0b14fe1d6c456be31a3918d196ac/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727072457"